dire adieu aux sorties et aux piscines.

147
00:10:16,867 --> 00:10:18,327
Oh, oh.

148
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:20,495
Oui. Pas si cool, hein ?

149
00:10:22,998 --> 00:10:26,585
